'''2015年聖貝納迪諾槍擊案'''，又稱'''2015年加州愛伊槍擊案''' 、'''2015年南加州槍擊案'''。2015年12月2日，美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[內陸帝國|內陸帝國]]（俗稱[[愛伊|愛伊]]）[[圣贝纳迪诺_(加利福尼亚州)|圣贝纳迪诺]]的内陆区域中心（Inland Regional Center）发生了一起枪击案，造成14人死亡、21人受伤。<ref name="cnbc">{{cite web|last1=Rosenfeld|first1=Everette|title=At least 3 confirmed dead in San Bernardino, Calif. mass shooting|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2015/12/02/authorities-responding-to-reports-of-mass-shooting-in-san-bernardino-california-nbc-los-angeles.html|publisher=CNBC|accessdate=December 2, 2015|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202223127/http://www.cnbc.com/2015/12/02/authorities-responding-to-reports-of-mass-shooting-in-san-bernardino-california-nbc-los-angeles.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>數小時後在案發地點附近兩名槍手與警方駁火，槍戰中該兩人被擊斃，兩名警員受傷。<ref name="NYTDay1">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/03/us/san-bernardino-shooting.html |title=San Bernardino Shooting Kills at Least 14; Two Suspects Are Dead |date=2015-12-03 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210194831/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/03/us/san-bernardino-shooting.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first1=Ashley |last1=Soley-Cerro |first2=Steve |last2=Kuzj |first3=Melissa |last3=Pamer |url=http://ktla.com/2015/12/03/san-bernardino-shooting-suspects-were-reportedly-married-motive-sought/ |title=Majority of San Bernardino Shooters' Victims Were County Employees: Police Chief |publisher=KTLA |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212075819/http://ktla.com/2015/12/03/san-bernardino-shooting-suspects-were-reportedly-married-motive-sought/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在上午十一点有911急救电话报警。初時警方消息称，大约有三名嫌疑犯，穿着类似军用的防弹衣。一男一女共两人在与警方的交火中丧生，另外一人被擒获。<ref>{{Cite web|title = At Least 14 People Killed In Shooting In San Bernardino, Calif.|url = http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/12/02/458196942/active-shooter-situation-reported-in-san-bernardino-calif|website = NPR.org|accessdate = 2015-12-03|archive-date = 2015-12-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203101614/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/12/02/458196942/active-shooter-situation-reported-in-san-bernardino-calif|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title = San Bernardino shooting live updates: 14 killed; at least 1 suspect 'down' after police shootout|url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-san-bernardino-shooting-live-updates-htmlstory.html|newspaper = Los Angeles Times|access-date = 2015-12-03|issn = 0458-3035|archive-date = 2015-12-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203001057/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-san-bernardino-shooting-live-updates-htmlstory.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>後來警方表示第三名疑犯與本案無關，只是涉及不相干的輕微罪行。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-san-bernardino-suspects-sprayed-the-room-with-bullets-20151203-story.html |title=San Bernardino suspects 'sprayed the room with bullets' |work=LA Times |date=2015-12-04 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206025614/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-san-bernardino-suspects-sprayed-the-room-with-bullets-20151203-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==背景==
圣贝纳迪诺消防局通过[[Twitter|Twitter]]发布消息，警方正在处理沃特曼大道（Waterman Avenue）1300号的案发现场。<ref name=SBF>{{Cite tweet|author= San Bernardino Fire Department |user=SBCityFire |number= 672131690978906112|date= 2 December 2015|title= SBFD units responding to reports of 20 victim shooting incident in 1300 block of S. Waterman. SBPD is working to clear the scene.}}</ref><ref name=Siemaszko>{{cite news|last1=Siemaszko|first1=Corey|title=Authorities Respond to Report of Shooting in San Bernardino, California|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/authorities-respond-report-shooting-san-bernardino-california-n472976|accessdate=December 2, 2015|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date=December 2, 2015|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202193953/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/authorities-respond-report-shooting-san-bernardino-california-n472976|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Whitcomb>{{cite news|last1=Whitcomb|first1=Dan|title=Reports of 20 victims wounded in shooting in San Bernardino, California|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/12/02/us-california-shooting-idUSKBN0TL2F120151202|accessdate=December 2, 2015|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=December 2, 2015|archive-date=2015-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203004135/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/12/02/us-california-shooting-idUSKBN0TL2F120151202|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=KTVU>{{cite news|title=Up to 20 victims reported at active shooting in San Bernardino|url=http://www.ktvu.com/news/55237712-story|accessdate=December 2, 2015|publisher=[[KTVU|KTVU]]|date=December 2, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203004200/http://www.ktvu.com/news/55237712-story|archive-date=2015-12-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>沃特曼大道和帕克环路（Park Circle Drive）被警方封闭，并督促司机远离此区域。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Multiple-Victims-Reported-in-San-Bernardino-Shooting-360080371.html|title=Authorities Respond to Active Shooter in San Bernardino|work=NBC Southern California|accessdate=2015-12-02|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202205740/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Multiple-Victims-Reported-in-San-Bernardino-Shooting-360080371.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==位置==
早期报道称内陆区域中心是枪击案的案发地点，<ref name="wash_Acti">{{Cite web | title = Active shooter reported in San Bernardino, Calif.; authorities say multiple suspects, victims | last = Berman | first = Mark | work = Washington Post | date = December 2, 2015 | accessdate = December 2, 2015 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2015/12/02/police-in-san-bernadino-calif-responding-report-of-shooting/ | language =  | quote =  | archive-date = 2015-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151202223101/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2015/12/02/police-in-san-bernadino-calif-responding-report-of-shooting/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>它是一个帮助发育残疾人士的非盈利机构，<ref>{{Cite web|title = Inland Regional Center|url = http://inlandrc.org/|date = April 30, 2015|accessdate = December 2, 2015|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150430005256/http://inlandrc.org/|archivedate = 2015年4月30日}}</ref><ref name="nbcn_SanB">{{Cite web | title = San Bernardino Shooting: What Is the Inland Regional Center? | last = Chuck | first = Elizabeth | work = NBC News | date = December 2, 2015 | accessdate = December 2, 2015 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/san-bernardino-shooting-what-inland-regional-center-n473016 | quote =  | archive-date = 2015-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151202204441/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/san-bernardino-shooting-what-inland-regional-center-n473016 | dead-url = no }}</ref>位于南沃特曼大街1365号。<ref name="ABC7">{{Cite web|title = 12 people killed in shooting at San Bernardino social services facility|url = http://abc7.com/news/san-bernardino-firefighters-respond-to-reports-of-multiple-victim-shooting/1106844/|website = ABC7 Los Angeles|accessdate = December 2, 2015|archive-date = 2015-12-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203003958/http://abc7.com/news/san-bernardino-firefighters-respond-to-reports-of-multiple-victim-shooting/1106844/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==案發經過==
槍手賽義德·法魯克（Syed Farook）和塔什芬·馬利克（Tashfeen Malik）在12月2日早上聲稱出門看醫生，把6個月大女兒交托法魯克的母親照顧後離開。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/dec/03/san-bernadino-shooting-suspects-syed-rizwan-farook-tashfeen-malik |title=San Bernardino shooting: what we know about the suspects |first=Paul |last=Lewis |work=The Guardian |date=2015-12-03 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151209184303/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/dec/03/san-bernadino-shooting-suspects-syed-rizwan-farook-tashfeen-malik |dead-url=no }}</ref>法魯克工作的環境衛生局當日在案發地點舉行聚會，法魯克也有出席。法魯克半途離開，後來帶同妻子馬利克返回，二人身穿黑色戰鬥服和戴上滑雪面罩，在上午10:59用非法改造的[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]和[[半自動步槍|半自動步槍]]向人們開槍。整個開槍過程不長於4分鐘。

二人在警察抵達前離開現場。目擊者說他們憑槍手的聲線和體型認出其中一人是法魯克。<ref name=NPRIdentify>{{cite news|last1=Dean Hopkins|first1=Christopher|first2=Laura|last2=Wagner|title=Police Identify Suspects Killed After Deadly San Bernardino Shooting|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/12/02/458196942/active-shooter-situation-reported-in-san-bernardino-calif|accessdate=2015-12-03|publisher=[[NPR|NPR]]|date=2015-12-03|archive-date=2015-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203101614/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/12/02/458196942/active-shooter-situation-reported-in-san-bernardino-calif|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==警方行动==
警察和[[特種武器和戰術部隊|特種部隊]]包围了案发的建筑，并撤离了其中的人员。<ref name="CBC">{{Cite web|title = 20 victims reportedly wounded in San Bernardino, Calif., shooting|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mass-shooting-san-bernardino-california-1.3347432|website = www.cbc.ca|accessdate = December 2, 2015|archive-date = 2015-12-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203024616/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mass-shooting-san-bernardino-california-1.3347432|dead-url = no}}</ref>执法部门得悉法魯克是疑兇後，追寻他在案發前租用的一辆黑色[[SUV|SUV]]。<ref>{{cite web|title = SUV in San Bernardino shooting had Utah tags, was rented in California|url = http://fox13now.com/2015/12/02/officials-at-least-20-victims-in-san-bernardino-mass-shooting/|publisher = Fox 13|location = Salt Lake City|accessdate = 2015-12-06|archive-date = 2015-12-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151206140204/http://fox13now.com/2015/12/02/officials-at-least-20-victims-in-san-bernardino-mass-shooting/|dead-url = no}}</ref>下午大約3時，警方終於截停該輛黑色SUV，法魯克和馬利克在車上向警員開槍，警員還擊，槍戰歷時約1分鐘，二人最終被擊斃。

==受害者==
受害者被送到邻近的{{le|罗马琳达大学医学中心|Loma Linda University Medical Center}}<ref name="CBC" />和{{le|箭头区域医疗中心|Arrowhead Regional Medical Center}}。

==行兇者==
被警方擊斃的兩人分別是28歲男子賽義德·法魯克和其27歲妻子塔什芬·馬利克。賽義德·法魯克是[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，<ref name=dailymail20151203/>出生於芝加哥，是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]移民的第二代，在聖貝納迪諾當地環境衛生局擔任巡視員。馬利克是巴基斯坦人，曾在[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]居住，她通過與法魯克結婚而取得K-1未婚配偶簽證入境美國。<ref name=xh20151205>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-12/05/c_128500401.htm |title=揭秘加州血案夫妻档枪手：精心准备 家藏弹药库 |publisher=新華網 |date=2015-12-05 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212130400/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-12/05/c_128500401.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

二人在行兇前曾多次到靶场练习射击。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/voa-news-us-shooting-20151208/3093231.html |title=美联调局：加州枪杀案夫妇早已被激进化 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2015-12-08 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210105120/http://www.voachinese.com/content/voa-news-us-shooting-20151208/3093231.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

警方事後在二人的車和家中搜出數千發子彈和一些爆炸裝置及製造工具。<ref name=xh20151205/>馬利克被發現曾經在[[臉書|臉書]]以非真名向[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]首領[[阿布·贝克尔·巴格达迪|巴格達迪]]宣誓效忠。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/12/151204_us_california_shooter_is |title=美国警方以“恐怖主义行为”调查加州枪击案 |work=BBC中文網 |date=2015-12-04 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151207034134/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/12/151204_us_california_shooter_is |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在私下與妻子的私人網路討論中涉及殉道與聖戰思想。

法魯克的鄰居在案發前已察覺他倆有可疑行為，例如近期突然有許多速遞包裹送抵，以及深夜在車房進行不明工作，不過鄰居擔心被指責為[[種族歧視|種族歧視]]而不敢向當局舉報。<ref name=xh20151205/><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3344736/Neighbors-Saudi-husband-wife-San-Bernardino-shooters-noticed-acting-suspiciously-did-NOT-report-fear-racial-profiling.html |title=Neighbors of San Bernardino shooters 'noticed them acting suspiciously' |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2015-12-04 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151209154331/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3344736/Neighbors-Saudi-husband-wife-San-Bernardino-shooters-noticed-acting-suspiciously-did-NOT-report-fear-racial-profiling.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反應==
[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的支持者在網上慶祝本次槍擊案。<ref name=dailymail20151203>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3343882/Intelligence-officials-hunt-link-terror-groups-ISIS-praise-San-Bernardino-attack-left-14-dead-17-injured.html |title=Hunt for link to terror groups as ISIS praise San Bernardino attack |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2015-12-03 |accessdate=2015-12-03 |archive-date=2015-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203110336/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3343882/Intelligence-officials-hunt-link-terror-groups-ISIS-praise-San-Bernardino-attack-left-14-dead-17-injured.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

